# =============================================================================
# toys monorepo — track CODE on GitHub; keep WORK local (see GIT_WORKFLOW.md)
# =============================================================================

# --- Python / tooling (everywhere) ---
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.eggs/
**/dist/
**/build/

# --- IDE / OS ---
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- anisotropy: local research work (never publish) ---
anisotropy/*.pdb
anisotropy/*.ply
anisotropy/*.npz
anisotropy/**/*.pdb
anisotropy/**/*.ply
anisotropy/**/*.npz
anisotropy/**/*.mrc
anisotropy/**/*.mrcs
anisotropy/**/*.log
anisotropy/orientation_diagnostics/
anisotropy/_test*/
anisotropy/_tmp*/
anisotropy/*.png
!anisotropy/docs/**/*.png

# --- toys/ cryo projection subproject (local data) ---
toys/**/*.mrc
toys/**/*.mrcs
toys/**/*.star
toys/datasets/
toys/output/

# ff19SB upstream test suite (not needed at runtime)
anisotropy/utils/ff19SB_201907-master/**/test/

# Sphinx build
anisotropy/docs/_build/
